{"tid":2033077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家成日提人退場要點變裝點潛走，有冇諗過入場唔小心都會收皮？","createTime":"2020-05-24T12:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T12:59:06.000Z","uid":148315,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9845646a18c72698bf6157ac791392e00dde2a38","tid":2033077,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"即係如果你由出門口到落場做嘢嘅時候<br />\n如果完全冇變過裝<br />\n咁你事後退場時變裝意義不大<br />\n<br />\n狗狗可以憑你事發衣著查附近嘅cctv<br />\n沿住你可能嘅入場路線查cctv一直track住<br />\n睇到你喺邊度行過/上落車<br />\nTrack到你喺棟樓嘅升降機出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以如果你冇隱蔽哋變完裝先入場<br />\n麻煩做特別嘢時停一停諗一諗<br />\n忍一忍手<br />\n交畀其他手足跟進</span></span>"},{"pid":"cda9eaafdcc7d400e7abd6e847868ef4ff52ccf7","tid":2033077,"uid":148315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:21:27.000Z","msg":"例如你本身斯只係去和平示威<br />\n冇專登變裝<br />\n但見到街邊有藍絲串柒柒，仲要搬開啲路障<br />\n你好嬲想埋去揼柒佢之前<br />\n唔該諗一諗你安全措施做足未<br />\n同埋承唔承受到個風險"},{"pid":"d572c82b32be047ad564e326d02857a8e4e734d8","tid":2033077,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"297a578b067488bed36130ad3d7a7c58fbae0bd6","tid":2033077,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c029e5ab2d107902fb39f13b5a6696d9bd1527e7","tid":2033077,"uid":142517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"推 入場前要變身先 如果唔係其實已經經過好多cam既洗禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c92289e211cde4d0b5e4e1b48594735bede615","tid":2033077,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a08d3ca8ce113044bbf827b5619e16164b9564de","tid":2033077,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse